# Build context is the repo root (needed for the pnpm workspace + single root
# lockfile). Keep the context lean: ship only what `pnpm build` needs.

# Node
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.vite
**/.verify
*.tsbuildinfo

# VCS / CI / tooling
.git
.github
.claude
backlog

# Go backend (not part of the frontend image)
cmd
internal
migrations
*.go
go.mod
go.sum

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
